cps.api.request

Interface RequestHandler<SessionType>

  • Type Parameters:
    SessionType - the generic type of the user session
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ServerController

    public interface RequestHandler<SessionType>
    Is used to implement request dispatching. Each request class has a handle() method which receives an object that implements this interface. The class-specific method calls a handler method of the appropriate type for that class.
